pillow%20once%20every%20three%20nights.%20It%20fluffed%20back%20into%20place%2C%20good%20as%20new.%20My%20head%20and%20neck%20always%20felt%20supported%2C%20and%20I%20never%20awoke%20with%20any%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20main%20benefits%20of%20down%20alternative%20pillows%20is%20that%20they're%20hypoallergenic.%20Unlike%20real%20down%2C%20which%20can%20aggravate%20allergies%2C%20down%20alternative%20pillows%20are%20a%20mix%20of%20microfiber.%20Parachute%20uses%20recycled%20polyester%20with%20a%20cotton%20shell%20for%20a%20plush%20feel.%20For%20stomach%20sleepers%20with%20allergies%2C%20I%20especially%20recommend%20down%20alternative%20pillows%20because%20you'll%20get%20all%20of%20the%20benefits%20of%20down%20without%20prompting%20any%20flare-ups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22038f4f30-dc2d-4e26-8652-6d58cbd5a6aa%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%5C%22%3EBest%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20mere%20two-and-a-half-inch%20loft%2C%20the%20Belly%20Sleep%20Pillow%20is%20the%20thinnest%20pillow%20we've%20tried.%20It's%20stomach%20sleepers%20who%20have%20been%20tempted%20to%20sleep%20without%20a%20pillow%20and%20simply%20lie%20flat%20on%20the%20mattress.%20It's%20cooling%2C%20supportive%2C%20and%20uniquely%20designed%20for%20those%20of%20us%20who%20sleep%20on%20our%20stomachs%2C%20and%20it%20costs%20under%20%2450.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Belly%20Sleeper%20pillow%20is%20made%20with%20a%20layer%20of%20memory%20foam%20and%20cooling%20gel%2C%20surrounded%20by%20a%20removable%2C%20machine-washable%20cover.%20I%20was%20intimidated%20by%20the%20pillow%20at%20first%20%E2%80%94%20it%20has%20a%20low%20profile%20that's%20unlike%20any%20other%20pillow%20I've%20ever%20used%20and%20is%20only%20available%20in%20a%20queen-size.%20It%20looked%20certifiably%20strange%20in%20my%20king-size%20pillowcase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20lying%20on%20my%20stomach%2C%20the%20low%20loft%20kept%20my%20back%20perfectly%20straight%2C%20with%20my%20spine%20aligned.%20Stomach%2