0medium-firm%20for%20a%20little%20extra%20support%2C%20but%20since%20there%20is%20a%20low-loft%20version%20(4%20inches%20for%20the%20standard%20and%204.3%20inches%20for%20the%20king%20size)%2C%20my%20spine%20stayed%20aligned%20while%20the%20memory%20foam%20supported%20my%20head%20and%20neck.%20The%20memory%20foam%20molded%20to%20my%20head%20and%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20other%20low-loft%20pillows%2C%20this%20pillow%20looks%20silly%20in%20a%20pillowcase.%20And%2C%20if%20you%20like%20a%20soft%20pillow%2C%20this%20might%20be%20too%20firm%20for%20you.%20For%20soft%2C%20cooling%20pillows%2C%20I'd%20opt%20for%20breathable%20down%20or%20down%20alternative%20pillows%20like%20the%20Parachute%20Down%20Alternative%20Pillow%20or%20the%20Brooklinen%20Down%20Pillow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226b68b108-dac7-4cf0-a035-74d375875941%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20neck%20pain%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20neck%20pain%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20us%20stomach%20sleepers%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20ensure%20that%20we're%20doing%20everything%20we%20can%20to%20keep%20neck%20pain%20at%20bay.%20A%20misaligned%20spine%20is%20the%20most%20common%20culprit%20for%20neck%20pain%20while%20sleeping%2C%20which%20happens%20when%20your%20body%20isn't%20supported%20and%20your%20neck%20is%20lying%20at%20an%20angle.%20%26quot%3BYour%20pillow%20plays%20a%20big%20role%20in%20spinal%20alignment%2C%26quot%3B%20Murray%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20wrong%20one%20can%20leave%20you%20with%20neck%20pain%2C%20disrupted%20sleep%2C%20and%20leave%20you%20feeling%20achy%20the%20next%20day.%26quot%3B%20This%20is%20a%20frequent%20problem%20when%20stomach%20sleepers%20use%20a%20high-loft%20pillow%2C%20five%20inches%20or%20more%2C%20since%20your%20back%20and%20neck%20aren't%20in%20line.%20Stomach%20sleepers%20need%20a%20low-profile%20pillow%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-pillow-for-neck-pain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavoid%20neck%20pain.%3C%2F