0suggesting%20investor%20sentiment%20is%20abnormally%20elevated.%20Excitement%20around%20AI%20has%20also%20driven%20up%20market%20valuations%20to%20levels%20consistent%20with%20prior%20major%20bubbles%2C%20like%20those%20seen%20in%201929%20and%202000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETom%20Essaye%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Sevens%20Report%20whose%20clients%20include%20advisors%20at%20some%20of%20Wall%20Street's%20biggest%20firms%2C%20recently%20addressed%20the%20topic%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20client%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20bubble%20in%20modern%20market%20history%20has%20been%20based%20on%20a%20narrative%2C%20whether%20it%20be%20the%20internet%20or%20real%20estate.%20Critically%2C%20that%20given%20narrative%20is%20widely%20perceived%20by%20the%20investment%20world%20to%20be%20a%20source%20of%20unlimited%20earnings%20growth%20across%20most%20market%20sectors%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20an%20August%201%20note.%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20that%20potentially%20bubble-inflating%20theme%20is%20unquestionably%20AI%20technology.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Essaye%20sees%20it%2C%20the%20best%20way%20to%20measure%20the%20health%20of%20the%20AI%20trade%20is%20to%20look%20at%20how%20semiconductor%20stocks%20overall%20are%20behaving%2C%20as%20chips%20are%20the%20lifeblood%20of%20AI%20technology.%20One%20can%20do%20this%20using%20the%20PHLX%20Semiconductor%20Index%20(SOX)%2C%20a%20group%20of%2030%20stocks%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComparing%20the%20index's%20performance%20to%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20shows%20%26quot%3Bthis%20bull%20market%20in%20equities%20has%20a%20serious%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20concern%20for%20Essaye%20is%20that%20SOX%20still%20sits%20below%20its%20July%202024%20highs%20while%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20has%20risen%20by%20almost%2014%25%20over%20that%20time.%20This%20suggests%20the%20market's%20rally%2C%20which%20is%20largely%20being%20fueled%20by%20the%20AI%20narrative%2C%20could%20be%20in%20an%20unhealthy%20place%20if%20many%20AI%20stocks%20themselves%20are%20failing%20to%20keep%20up%20their%20momentum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20takeaway%20here%20is%20that%20if%20AI%20remains%20the%20primary%20source%20of%20bullish%20optimism%20for%20a%20continued%20rally%20in%20the%20broader%20stock%20market%20in%20the%20months%20and%20quarters%20ahead%2C%20this%20market%20is%20in%20trouble%20and%20at%20risk%20of%20rolling%20over%20sooner%20than%20later%20as%20the%20SOX%20should%20still%20be%20leading%20the%20market%20higher%20like%20it%20was%20in%202024%2C%20not%20lagging%20considerably%20over%20the%20last%2012%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThat%20divergence%20in%20index%20performance%20is%20meaningful%2C%20and%20if%20we%20see%20the%20SOX%20roll%20over%20in%20the%20weeks%20or%20months%20ahead%20and%20start%20selling%20off%20materially%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20will%20almost%20certainly%20not%20be%20far%20behind.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20performance%20of%20an%20ETF%20that%20tracks%20the%20SOX%20index%20over%20the%20last%20three%20years%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SOXQ%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68963a42f748d8c055f72c9a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221296%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20performance%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22s%26amp%3Bp500%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68964699cfc04e97619b21a1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221276%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20sign%20of%20a%20potential%20bubble%2C%20and%20perhaps%20of%20trouble%20ahead%20for%20stocks%2C%20is%20that%20the%20US%20economic%20outlook%20appears%20to%20be%20weakening%2C%20Essaye%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBub