20alternative.%20The%20relocation%20will%20require%20a%20slow%20and%20long%20term%20plan%2C%20and%20we%20are%20exploring%20solutions%20to%20suggest%20to%20the%20officials%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ravindran%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20uncertain%20future%20for%20the%20deer%2C%20Gurusamy%20says%20that%20he%20will%20continue%20to%20protect%20the%20wildlife.%20%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20need%20any%20support%20and%20will%20fight%20with%20the%20farmers%20for%20the%20deer%E2%80%99s%20safety.%20The%20state%20government%20has%20sanctioned%20an%20irrigation%20pipeline%20to%20address%20the%20water%20woes%20for%20the%20farmers.%20Access%20to%20water%20may%20increase%20threats%20for%20deer%2C%20and%20hence%20an%20urgent%20solution%20is%20needed%20to%20reduce%20conflict%20between%20humans%20and%20wildlife.%20It%20would%20be%20appreciated%20if%20some%20experts%20help%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20images%20courtesy%3A%20R%20Gurusamy%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754649000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-07T123128.971-1754556152.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D483087%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22R%20Gurusamy%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20gave%20up%20most%20of%20his%20ancestral%20land%20to%20care%20for%20a%20few%20wandering%20deer%20in%20the%20vicinity.%20Today%2C%20even%20amid%20water%20and%20food%20shortage%20in%20the%20nearby%20forest%2C%20his%20land%20is%20a%20safe%20haven%20for%20over%201%2C800%20deer%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Himanshu%20Nitnaware%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F483087%2Ftamil-nadu-farmer-deer-conservation-1800-wildlife%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex-Teacher%20Turns%20Rooftop%20Into%20Dhaba%2C%20Serves%20Traditional%20Haryanvi%20Food%20Cooked%20Over%20Fire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22