wasn%E2%80%99t%20to%20work%20for%20corporations.%20As%20a%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20responsibility%20to%20give%20back%20to%20my%20roots%20and%20help%20sustain%20our%20generational%20farm.%20After%20all%2C%20it%20was%20the%20income%20from%20farming%20that%20provided%20for%20my%20education%20and%20that%20of%20my%20siblings%2C%E2%80%9D%20Saravanan%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishnasudha%20too%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20on%20a%20farm%2C%20always%20wished%20to%20retain%20the%20lush%20greenery%20that%20a%20farm%20life%20offered.%20This%20was%20a%20pact%20that%20they%20drew%20when%20they%20first%20met%20each%20other%20for%20marriage%2C%20she%20laughs.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20both%20wanted%20to%20return%20to%20the%20farm%20after%20working%20for%20a%20few%20years%20in%20corporate%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20thought%20in%20mind%2C%20the%20couple%20quit%20their%20jobs%20and%20returned%20to%20Palakkad%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20they%E2%80%99ve%20achieved%20and%20how%20they%E2%80%99ve%20transformed%20their%20farm%20since%20is%20an%20inspiring%20lesson%20for%20many.%20By%20leveraging%20technology%20for%20good%2C%20they%20mechanised%20the%20entire%20farming%20process%2C%20from%20creating%20natural%20fertilisers%20to%20setting%20up%20efficient%20irrigation%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20they%20developed%20value-added%20products%20like%20coconut%20oil%20and%20ghee%2C%20all%20produced%20at%20their%20farm%2C%20Deesan%20Farms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20model%20organic%20farm%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaravanan%E2%80%99s%20family%20owns%2036%20acres%20of%20land%20where%20they%20primarily%20grew%20coconuts.%20Although%20they%20practised%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352674%2Fgrow-bags-growing-vegetables-eyyo-kuriakose-kottayam-kerala-organic-farming-drip-ir