0the%20agriculture%20sector.%20Although%20Calvin%20went%20on%20to%20work%20in%20Bengaluru%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20Farish%20started%20a%20small%20seafood%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20his%20work%2C%20Farish%20says%20he%20learnt%20about%20the%20various%20issues%20faced%20by%20farmers%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level.%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20that%20farmers%20were%20facing%20a%20lot%20of%20challenges%20in%20making%20farming%20profitable%20due%20to%20climate%20change.%20I%20talked%20to%20more%20farmers%20and%20came%20to%20know%20the%20gravity%20of%20problems%20faced%20by%20them%20on%20a%20regular%20basis%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Calvin%20and%20Farish%20aimed%20to%20boost%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%20and%20resilience%20against%20climate%20fluctuations.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361736%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECalvin%20and%20Farish%20aimed%20to%20boost%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%20and%20resilience%20against%20climate%20fluctuations.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcapt